
Established in 1795, based in Winterthur.

The world's leading supplier of systems for short-staple fibre spinning.

Develops and manufactures machinery, systems and components used to convert natural and manmade fibres and their blends into yarns.

The only supplier worldwide to cover spinning preparation processes as well as all *four end spinning processes* currently established on the market.

Three business groups:
  • Machines and systems
  • After sales
  • Components

15 manufacturing locations in 9 countries.

Ca. 5000 employees of which 20 % in Switzerland.

